[
    {
        "text": "We treat this place and\nthose objects ",
        "start": 43.176,
        "duration": 2.336
    },
    {
        "text": "as historical documents.",
        "start": 45.512,
        "duration": 3.069
    },
    {
        "text": "I believe it is very\nimportant to keep this",
        "start": 48.581,
        "duration": 4.338
    },
    {
        "text": "and to let the visitors\nsee it and touch it.",
        "start": 52.919,
        "duration": 5.038
    },
    {
        "text": "This is the oldest part of\nthis camp.",
        "start": 65.732,
        "duration": 2.836
    },
    {
        "text": "And these are buildings built \nby the forced labor",
        "start": 68.568,
        "duration": 3.904
    },
    {
        "text": "of Soviet prisoners of war,\nduring 1941 and '42.",
        "start": 72.472,
        "duration": 5.806
    },
    {
        "text": "One of the most serious \nreasons for deterioration",
        "start": 79.913,
        "duration": 4.905
    },
    {
        "text": "is a very poor manufacturing\ntechnique.",
        "start": 84.818,
        "duration": 3.436
    },
    {
        "text": "The buildings in Birkenau,",
        "start": 88.254,
        "duration": 1.936
    },
    {
        "text": "they were built in a very fast\nway, in very bad conditions.",
        "start": 90.19,
        "duration": 5.472
    },
    {
        "text": "There is no memorial that\nwill give you",
        "start": 111.544,
        "duration": 4.071
    },
    {
        "text": "the image of the conditions\nin the camp.",
        "start": 115.615,
        "duration": 3.804
    },
    {
        "text": "You can only see it by\nseeing authentic buildings,",
        "start": 121.054,
        "duration": 4.504
    },
    {
        "text": "authentic space,\nauthentic elements.",
        "start": 125.558,
        "duration": 3.37
    },
    {
        "text": "And still what happened\nin this place ",
        "start": 128.928,
        "duration": 3.304
    },
    {
        "text": "is beyond our imagination.",
        "start": 132.232,
        "duration": 2.602
    },
    {
        "text": "But at least the authentic\nplace",
        "start": 134.834,
        "duration": 3.103
    },
    {
        "text": "can bring you closer\nto this history.",
        "start": 137.937,
        "duration": 2.369
    }
]